The shields are currently down so that Maximals can get to the 
meeting.

::Zardus::

Zardus looks over at Dark Angel as the bot comes up to him and asks 
for orders.

"A new bot is sending out a trasmission to get picked up," he says to 
Dark Angel, "Can you go and try to recruit him?"
